section.div: Web-based admin dashboard for Unispect, built with React and Vite. Enables property managers and staff to manage inspections, users, reporting, and configuration through a secure browser interface.

Terraform enables you to safely and predictably create, change, and improve infrastructure. It is a source-available tool that codifies APIs into declarative configuration files that can be shared amongst team members, treated as code, edited, reviewed, and versioned.
Unispect - A modern, offline-first mobile inspection app with photo-video uploads, notes, and PDF reporting.
